	<contentText >
		<text  position="relative" width="900px" height="auto" left="0" top="0px" ><![CDATA[Sandy, one of Emma’s colleagues, is on her way to see one of Emma’s properties, when she gets in a car accident. Emma goes to visit her in the hospital.]]></text>
	</contentText>
