		<strip id="2">
			<stripThumImg numberText="2" >
				<img path="content/images/ltr/module10/m10c02/m10c02s10/Page_10_Tumb_02.png" minwidth="700" minheight="550" />
				<title><![CDATA[]]></title>
			</stripThumImg>
			<stripBackground>				
				<img path="content/images/ltr/module10/m10c02/m10c02s10/Page_10_Strip_02.png" minwidth="700" minheight="550" ><![CDATA[]]></img>	
			</stripBackground>
			<stripCallOut align="right" isThoughtbubble="false" >
				<callOut minwidth="700" minheight="550" x="95" y="42" width="170" />
				<text ><![CDATA[Sandy, how are you doing?]]></text>
			</stripCallOut>
			<stripCallOut align="left" isThoughtbubble="false" >
				<callOut minwidth="700" minheight="550" x="578" y="100" width="170" arrowStyle="top:70px;" />
				<text ><![CDATA[Ugh, not so great. I keep replaying the accident in my mind – it seems like it came out of nowhere.  This guy totally ran the red light, and the police told me he was texting while driving.]]></text>
			</stripCallOut>
		</strip>
		
		<strip id="3">
			<stripThumImg numberText="3" >	
				<img path="content/images/ltr/module10/m10c02/m10c02s10/Page_10_Tumb_03.png" minwidth="700" minheight="550" />
				<title><![CDATA[]]></title>
			</stripThumImg>
			<stripBackground>				
				<img path="content/images/ltr/module10/m10c02/m10c02s10/Page_10_Strip_03.png" minwidth="700" minheight="550" ><![CDATA[]]></img>		
			</stripBackground>
			<stripCallOut align="right" isThoughtbubble="false" >
				<callOut minwidth="700" minheight="550" x="95" y="42" width="170" />
				<text ><![CDATA[I’m so sorry this happened. Your mom told me that you might need a few more surgeries on your leg.]]></text>
			</stripCallOut>
			<stripCallOut align="left" isThoughtbubble="false" >
				<callOut minwidth="700" minheight="550" x="578" y="50" width="170" arrowStyle="top:121px;" />
				<text ><![CDATA[Yes, that, plus a lot of physical therapy. But that's not the worst of it. The doctors think I may have a brain injury. I keep getting really painful headaches and my balance and coordination are a mess. I think I may be out of work for a while.]]></text>			
			</stripCallOut>
		</strip>
		
		<strip id="4">
			<stripThumImg numberText="4" >	
				<img path="content/images/ltr/module10/m10c02/m10c02s10/Page_10_Tumb_04.png" minwidth="700" minheight="550" />
				<title><![CDATA[]]></title>
			</stripThumImg>
			<stripBackground>				
				<img path="content/images/ltr/module10/m10c02/m10c02s10/Page_10_Strip_04.png" minwidth="700" minheight="550" ><![CDATA[]]></img>		
			</stripBackground>
			<stripCallOut align="right" isThoughtbubble="false" >
				<callOut minwidth="700" minheight="550" x="129" y="57" width="140" arrowStyle="top:10px;" />
				<text ><![CDATA[Oh, that’s terrible, Sandy.]]></text>
			</stripCallOut>
		<stripCallOut align="bottomleft" isThoughtbubble="false" >
				<callOut minwidth="700" minheight="550" x="398" y="10" width="360" arrowStyle="left: 85px;" />
				<text ><![CDATA[The medical costs are so high, even with my health insurance. And I have no idea how long I'll be out of work. I don’t know how I’m going to pay for all this.]]></text>			
				<text ><![CDATA[My family has set up a fund to help with costs and I think they even set up a Facebook page, but I hate having to ask other people for help – I like to keep personal things private.]]></text>			
			</stripCallOut>
		</strip>

